  • public class TransitionProbability
extends Object
    Transition Probability class is based on the formulae introduced in my paper titled: Adaptive Model Learning for Continual Verification of Non-Functional Properties. It may also help to first read my paper titled: Using Observation Ageing to Improve Markovian Model Learning in QoS Engineering
